39:42.881 --> 39:45.093
JUST BE HONEST.

39:45.093 --> 39:47.305
DO YOU TRUST THE MAN?

39:57.355 --> 39:58.356
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

39:58.356 --> 40:01.359
NO, I DON'T.

40:01.359 --> 40:04.402
I MOVE TO TERMINATE HIM,
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY.

40:04.402 --> 40:07.195
IF THERE'S ONE THING
I'VE LEARNED OVER THE YEARS,

40:07.195 --> 40:12.330
IT'S THAT IT ONLY TAKES ONE
PERSON, ONE PATIENT, ONE MOMENT,

40:12.330 --> 40:15.033
TO CHANGE YOUR LIFE FOREVER --

40:15.033 --> 40:19.417
TO CHANGE YOUR PERSPECTIVE,
COLOR YOUR THINKING,

40:19.417 --> 40:23.672
TO FORCE YOU TO RE-EVALUATE
EVERYTHING YOU THINK YOU KNOW...

40:23.672 --> 40:28.046
