WHAT HAS HAPPENED TO YOU?

40:36.264 --> 40:39.558
DO YOU WANT TO LIVE THIS WAY?

40:39.558 --> 40:41.189
[ APPLAUSE ]

40:43.191 --> 40:45.984
Cristina: I'M SORRY, BUT
I HAVE TO ASK ONE MORE TIME.

40:45.984 --> 40:49.327
JASON...

40:49.327 --> 40:51.620
WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO REMOVE THE VENT?

40:51.620 --> 40:53.532
[ VENTILATOR HISSING ]

40:53.532 --> 40:55.453
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

41:09.387 --> 41:11.389
